===Noun===
'''막''' ([[幕]] mag, mak)

# [[tent]], [[hut]], [[shack]], [[shelter]]
# [[curtain]]
# [[act]] (of dramas) 

====Derived terms====
* [[움]]막 (ummag, -mak) [[dugout]] [[hut]]
* [[장막]] ([[帳幕]] jangmag, -mak) [[curtain]]
