===Verb===
'''막다''' (magda, makda)
# To [[stop up]]
# To [[enclose]], [[fence]], [[screen off]], [[shield]]
# To [[curb]], [[defend]], [[protect]]
# To [[keep]] (from doing), [[hinder]], [[prevent]]


====Derived terms====
* 막히다 (maghida, mak-) To be [[clogged]], [[blocked]]
* [[틀]]어막다 (teulEo-, teurEo-) To [[stuff]], [[stop up]] (a hollow, mouth, ear, etc., literally, "by turning" something forcibly into it.) 

